<para style="q1">

<verse number="20" style="v" />Rebuke has broken my heart; I am full of heaviness;</para>

<para style="q1">I looked for someone to take pity, but there was none;</para>

<para style="q1">I looked for comforters, but I found none.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="21" style="v" />They gave me poison for my food;</para>

<para style="q1">in my thirst they gave me vinegar to drink.</para>
